name: Jaane Tu... Ya Jaane Na
description: Two best friends being convinced that they are not in love search for each other's love.

name: Break Ke Baad
description: Aaliya is not ready for commitment even after a decade-long friendship with Abhay. She remains indifferent when he follows her to Australia, but is finally shaken when he announces his marriage.

name: Katti Batti
description: A man falls in love with a woman because of her outlook on life. They are in a relationship for five years until a sudden turn of events causes a problem in their relationship.

name: Kidnap
description: A fortnight before her eighteenth birthday, Sonia goes missing. Her family receives a call informing them that she has been kidnapped and her estranged father, a US-based businessman, must now follow the kidnapperâ€™s instructions to the letter if he is to entertain any hopes of seeing her alive again. Is this a mere kidnapping or is there more to it than what meets the eye?

name: Ek Main Aur Ekk Tu
description: Rahul and Riana meet each other for the first time, get drunk, and awake the next morning to find that they have gotten legally married to each other.

name: Luck
description: Born lucky, Karim Moussa takes to exploiting it instead of focusing on studies. Now a wealthy gambler, he decides to recruit about a dozen lucky people to participate in a deadly game of survival.

name: Mere Brother Ki Dulhan
description: A Mumbai man finds himself in an unpredictable situation when the prospective bride of his older brother is a woman he has history with.

name: Matru Ki Bijlee Ka Mandola
description: Harry is an industrialist who loves his daughter Bijlee, and the bond they share with Harry's man friday, Matru. Bijlee's plan to wed the son of a politician, however, brings twists and turns in the lives of Matru, Bijlee and Mandola.

name: Delhi Belly
description: Three unsuspecting, average guys find themselves on the hit list of one of India's most-powerful crime syndicates.

name: Gori Tere Pyaar Mein
description: Sriram Venkat is the most shallow guy on earth who doesn't value relationships, family, friends, life or the country. Not necessarily in that order. Because he couldn't care less about the order. This makes him the clear 'black' sheep of the family.

name: I Hate Luv Storys
description: Simran loves love stories, with her ideal job and perfect boyfriend, she lives a blissful and dreamy life. However, things are rudely interrupted by Jay's cynicism on sentimentality.
